overview: The user initiated a request to significantly enhance the aesthetic
  appeal of their sleep questionnaire application, which they felt was too
  generic. The approach involved a detailed analysis of the existing design,
  followed by a comprehensive implementation strategy. Key decisions included
  adopting a calming, sleep-themed color palette, redesigning the main form's
  layout with subtle background elements and an improved progress indicator, and
  transforming the welcome screen with engaging feature cards. All form
  components like checkboxes, radio buttons, and sliders were polished, and
  every section of the questionnaire, including the final report, was updated to
  ensure consistent and cohesive styling. During the review, a console error
  related to  values being passed to input fields was identified and
  resolved by modifying the  component to safely handle  values.
  The outcome is a visually appealing, professional, and user-friendly sleep
  health application with a consistent and calming aesthetic.
